NOW: SEPTEMBER 10, 2020

Fixed Ops Marketing Bootcamp

Virtual Livestream

9:00 am – 5:00 pm
[/vc_column_text][nectar_btn size=”medium” open_new_tab=”true” button_style=”regular” button_color_2=”Accent-Color” icon_family=”default_arrow” url=”https://www.accelevents.com/e/u/checkout/FixedOpsMarketingBootCamp/tickets/order” text=”Register Now”][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row type=”in_container” full_screen_row_position=”middle” column_margin=”default” scene_position=”center” text_color=”dark” text_align=”left” overlay_strength=”0.3″ shape_divider_position=”bottom” bg_image_animation=”none”][vc_column column_padding=”no-extra-padding” column_padding_position=”all” background_color_opacity=”1″ background_hover_color_opacity=”1″ column_link_target=”_self” column_shadow=”none” column_border_radius=”none” width=”1/1″ tablet_width_inherit=”default” tablet_text_alignment=”default” phone_text_alignment=”default” overlay_strength=”0.3″ column_border_width=”none” column_border_style=”solid” bg_image_animation=”none”][divider line_type=”No Line” custom_height=”32″][vc_video link=”https://youtu.be/hOsCYxiM6_4″ align=”center”][divider line_type=”No Line” custom_height=”32″][vc_column_text] Join Brian Pasch for his progressive one-day workshop where he is helping to provide the latest strategies that will increase your service revenue through messaging platforms and online marketing. If you are in fixed operations (Service Managers & Fixed Ops Directors) or marketing you will not want to miss this virtual livestream bootcamp. Brian will help you modernize any outdated Fixed Operations marketing strategies.

FIXED OPS DIGITAL is proud to sponsor such an event to help the department we focus all of our efforts on. Brian is a leader in the automotive marketing space and we are excited to see all that he is going to bring to this event.

Industry leaders are also being invited to the workshop so you can truly hear from the best sharing their winning strategies to elevate your department reach new heights.

“There are no prerequisites to attend other than a keen desire to increase the dealership’s service opportunities, revenue, and customer retention.”[/vc_column_text][divider line_type=”No Line” custom_height=”32″][vc_row_inner column_margin=”default” text_align=”left”][vc_column_inner column_padding=”no-extra-padding” column_padding_position=”all” centered_text=”true” background_color_opacity=”1″ background_hover_color_opacity=”1″ column_shadow=”none” column_border_radius=”none” column_link_target=”_self” width=”1/1″ tablet_width_inherit=”default” overlay_strength=”0.3″ column_border_width=”none” column_border_style=”solid” bg_image_animation=”none”][divider line_type=”No Line” custom_height=”32″][nectar_btn size=”medium” open_new_tab=”true” button_style=”regular” button_color_2=”Accent-Color” icon_family=”default_arrow” url=”https://www.accelevents.com/e/u/checkout/FixedOpsMarketingBootCamp/tickets/order” text=”Register Now”][divider line_type=”No Line” custom_height=”32″][vc_column_text]
